Package util

Class Tuple<K,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.Tuple<K,​V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - typeparemeter of the first entry in the tuple.
    V - typeparameter of the second entry in the tuple.
    public class Tuple<K,​V>
extends Object
    This class allows to store two values in a combined data structure (tuple, e.g. (ProductName, ProductPrice)). The types of the two values are generic so that the class can be reused.
